{"id": 1175, "genre": 1001, "title": "到底在哪些时刻，你深深地感受到了“丧”？", "description": "现代人的标志：累；现代年轻人的标志：累且颓废。（题图来自：dreamstime）", "record_count": 3970, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160819102314WuzrjdY3DnA4sxRJ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-08-19T17:00:14Z", "options": [{"id": 109312, "content": "好不容易周末，摊床上睡了一天，梦里各种被追，逃命。。。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647498}, {"id": 109057, "content": "哈哈哈哈 我现在躺在沙发吹着风扇吃着薯片当早餐我才不丧呢~", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147576}, {"id": 109058, "content": "想太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697079}, {"id": 109059, "content": "想太多", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697079}, {"id": 109315, "content": "没有钱的时候！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725226}, {"id": 109571, "content": "没有方向，没有目标，迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725608}, {"id": 110595, "content": "被爽约的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 679121}, {"id": 109060, "content": "放假没事干，在家里耗时间，每天都过着睡觉-起床-吃饭-再睡觉的生活", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718089}, {"id": 109316, "content": "平常忙到要死，感觉身体被掏空。周末一躺就起不来了……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668673}, {"id": 109573, "content": "给公司拍照，玉裂了缝，我得买下来，还要因此扣工资，钱已空", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 637381}, {"id": 137478, "content": "上班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689742}, {"id": 109062, "content": "完全不想上班，只想彻底宅，葛优瘫", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553583}, {"id": 109063, "content": "要开学了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719289}, {"id": 109575, "content": "对未来没有任何憧憬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725973}, {"id": 109064, "content": "生活方方面面同时经历低谷，同时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713212}, {"id": 109320, "content": "即将步入大学 学校里学霸很多竞争很大 感觉自己会落后 害怕人际关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725242}, {"id": 109065, "content": "想的很美好也很丰富，一觉醒来发现没有能力实现，内心焦灼却无从", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695336}, {"id": 109321, "content": "挂科的时候...啊啊啊啊啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 40841}, {"id": 109578, "content": "不断刷微信刷开心消消乐，还是觉得没劲，但又不想费脑子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725984}, {"id": 109067, "content": "想法很多 关键懒 不想动 感觉自己要废了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 678459}, {"id": 132876, "content": "周末，没有事情做的时候，想找一些事情做却又不想做的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830096}, {"id": 109068, "content": "每天过着倒的，越晚越清醒，越清醒越后悔，第二天又是一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 706615}, {"id": 109580, "content": "拖到没明天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725998}, {"id": 109070, "content": "刚准备去新岗位大干一番，就被肺炎送进了住院部，随之而来的是儿子的感冒及老婆出差，压力巨大", "image": "img/option/option/20160820164404QSP9HrWcUgAGvOap.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 260446}, {"id": 109071, "content": "感到跟颓废，不喜欢这种太过无忧无虑的生活，但是却没有意志去改", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716633}, {"id": 109072, "content": "和相爱的人被迫分开", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724342}, {"id": 109073, "content": "每天工作流程化又没有上升空间，觉得没有努力的方向和意义", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 654321}, {"id": 109074, "content": "宅，睡，吃如此度过一天的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 646712}, {"id": 109075, "content": "跟不会聊天的人聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724364}, {"id": 109076, "content": "买回来一本书，就看了十页\n但下回还会继续买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695355}, {"id": 109588, "content": "想太多，唯一不想动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690595}, {"id": 109844, "content": "都没兴趣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162244}, {"id": 109078, "content": "好累呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724375}, {"id": 109592, "content": "晚上回家，挂在外面的东西都被吹跑了???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726022}, {"id": 109081, "content": "不能回家！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 722501}, {"id": 109337, "content": "觉得给我一个月的休息却不知道做什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 689510}, {"id": 109338, "content": "想要对一个人好的机会都没有  ……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 725270}, {"id": 109083, "content": "每天逼自己     就这么～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702263}, {"id": 109339, "content": "微信上找她聊天，结果好几天没回我?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724643}, {"id": 110875, "content": "找不到活着的价值?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733095}, {"id": 109084, "content": "忙的要死不活的时候想着躺一天，真躺一天却被各种嘈杂搅得没睡着", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724407}, {"id": 109340, "content": "读了这么多年书，智商还是不够用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671494}, {"id": 109085, "content": "不想上班，只想打游戏、睡觉无限交替循环……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719854}, {"id": 109597, "content": "生活没目标，工作没动力，要勇气没勇气，要激情没激情，要葛优瘫还找不到合适的沙发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 715144}, {"id": 111645, "content": "想追女神，可是蛮王是她爸爸，寒冰是她妈妈，蔚是她姐姐，男刀是她弟弟，琴女是她闺蜜，ez是她前任，皇子是情敌，而我是蒙多。???", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738138}, {"id": 109086, "content": "对今天不满意，对明天没期待", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266081}, {"id": 111646, "content": "每一秒都觉得上一秒被荒废，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738138}, {"id": 109087, "content": "看人家一切都很轻松得到还表示不，自己却要经历艰难都不见的得到", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724407}, {"id": 111647, "content": "她不爱我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 738138}, {"id": 109088, "content": "好想和好哥们在一个公司，现实好残酷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692867}]}